            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                spiritus Athica <lb n="2"/>bonae <expan><abbr>memoria</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> dulcis <lb n="3"/>nomen anima mellea <lb n="4"/>petimus orationibus tuis <lb n="5"/>exaudiat <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> LXVII
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1: Die Wörter &amp;quot;&amp;quot;Spiritus Athica&amp;quot;&amp;quot; liegen zwischen 2 Christusmonogrammen. Z. 5: ein Christusmonogramm zwischen n(os) und vix(it).</p>
